name: JEMB Realty Corporation
description: JEMB Realty Corporation is a prominent real estate development and investment firm based in New York City. Founded in the early 1980s, the company specializes in the acquisition, development, and management of commercial and residential properties. With a strong commitment to innovation and sustainability, JEMB has developed a diversified portfolio that includes office buildings, retail spaces, and multifamily residential units. The firm is particularly known for its strategic partnerships and extensive knowledge of urban markets, allowing it to capitalize on emerging opportunities in high-demand areas. JEMB is dedicated to enhancing the urban landscape through thoughtful design and sustainable practices, aiming to create spaces that foster community interaction and enhance the quality of life for residents and visitors alike. The company's mission is to deliver long-term value to its stakeholders while positively impacting the communities it serves. With a focus on excellence and integrity, JEMB Realty continues to be a trusted name in the real estate industry, consistently striving to exceed expectations in every project it undertakes.
headquarters: New York City, New York, USA
